    <item>
      <title>英国警方警告暴徒，周三将发生更多骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方增派了警力，并表示如果极右翼活动分子按照网上流传的计划于周三晚聚集在移民中心，他们准备逮捕数百名极右翼活动分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
